{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_irene_set_1", "eventName": "燈火微明", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "燈火微明", "storyInfo": "艾麗妮做出了決定，來到老師墳前與老師道別。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g26_dusk_wild", "fadetime": 0.5, "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3, "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "BackgroundTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "duration": 30.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒼天，強風，原野，墓碑。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是所有大審判官的墳場。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾麗妮還記得，第一次被老師帶到這片墓園時的景象。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她沒敢告訴老師的是，當時的她心中被熱切的使命感填滿，犧牲對她來說是一種讚美。"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她因而覺得這片墓園被籠罩了一股神聖的美麗。"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g26_dusk_wild", "fadetime": 0.5, "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（好美。）", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#6$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾麗妮。", "name": "大審判官達里奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，我、我在，老師！", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你還是決定成為我的副手，那麼，從今天起，我不僅是你的老師，更是你的長官。", "name": "大審判官達里奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，長官！", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#6$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡，是我的導師在我成為審判官時，帶我來的地方。", "name": "大審判官達里奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#2"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的墳墓中大部分都是衣冠塚，畢竟，沒有多少審判官在死後能夠被找到完整的屍體。", "name": "大審判官達里奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#2"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而相比肉體，提燈與武器更能代表一名審判官存在過的痕跡。", "name": "大審判官達里奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#2"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因此，每一個犧牲在戰鬥中的審判官，他們的提燈和武器都會擺放在他們的墳前，以此作為紀念。", "name": "大審判官達里奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#2"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 50.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而這裡的九座墓碑，是九位聖徒的墓碑。", "name": "大審判官達里奧"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "九座......可是，您的老師，卡門閣下還健在吧？", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#2"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 50.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外八位聖徒在漫長的旅程中一一隕落，而卡門閣下也早已指定這裡作為他長眠的居所。", "name": "大審判官達里奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#2"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（如果我在捍衛伊比利亞的過程中犧牲，也能被葬在這裡，該有多好。）", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 50.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾麗妮。", "name": "大審判官達里奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是！", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 50.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將來有一天，你也會抱著我的提燈與武器來到這裡，將它們放在我的墳前。", "name": "大審判官達里奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 50.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到了那一刻，比起悲傷，我希望你已經明白了你戰鬥的意義。", "name": "大審判官達里奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為到了那時，將沒有人可以再教導你。", "name": "大審判官達里奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而在那之前，我會將我知道的一切都傳授給你。", "name": "大審判官達里奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.5, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾麗妮記得自己的回答是一句響亮的“是！”"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但當時的她尚不明白老師那些話的重量，也不明白生命的重量。"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到在斯圖提斐拉號上經歷了那一切，直到她如今抱著老師的提燈與武器，要將這些放在老師的墳前。"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的墓碑，又多了一些。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾麗妮走到一塊墓碑前。"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“大審判官達里奧，沉眠於此。”"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一塊木牌，一列簡單的句子，沒有任何額外的裝飾，這就是一個大審判官的墳墓。"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她輕輕地將老師的提燈與武器放在墓前，生怕驚擾到老師的靈魂，然後，緩緩坐下。"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師，這是您的提燈與武器。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照您的要求，我將它們放在您的墳前，這樣，您也算魂歸故土了。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，雖然我當時答應了您，卻沒想到，這一天來得這麼快。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使在那天之後已經過了一段時間，我也依然無法相信您已經離開。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，您終究是離開了。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會再有人呵斥我的幼稚，不會再有人告誡我要多想多看，不會再有人為我遮風擋雨了。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......算了，不說這些，如果您還在，聽到這些話也肯定會責備我的軟弱。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您放心，我還記得，您說，到了這一刻，希望我已經明白了我戰鬥的意義。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，我確實明白了一些。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......所以，未來一段時間，我可能不會來看您了。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這並不是因為我對自己的信仰產生了懷疑。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事實上，我正是因為真正理解了審判的含義，才做出了這個決定。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望您能看著我，老師。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.6, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡門閣下？！", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用緊張，站在這裡的，只是一個來為犧牲的學生上墳的老人罷了。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你放下的，是達里奧的東西吧。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是、是的，雖然原本不需要我來將這些放在老師墳前，但我特意去要來了。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟我是老師的學生，而且......也是對老師的告別。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#4$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼前的人是被冠以聖徒之名的大審判官，每一個審判官都應當知道，聖徒卡門經歷了多少考驗，又審判了多少邪惡。"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的存在，就是審判庭意志的化身。"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她有一瞬間後悔自己做出的決定，然而，她馬上壓下了這個想法。"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她早已決定。"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在來到這裡前，我去遞交了辭呈。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我打算辭去審判官的職務。所以，在離開審判庭前，我想要來這裡和老師告別。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾麗妮已經做好了被質問甚至責問的準備，然而，迎接她的，卻是聖徒的沉默。"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不敢揣測這沉默意味著什麼，但她並沒有從聖徒的身上感受到憤怒。"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "達里奧是我第八個學生，在我所有的學生中，他是最優秀的那一個。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，他不善言辭，即使在審判官中，他的人緣也不算好，即便是對我這個老師，也堅持用閣下來稱呼。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "做他的學生，你不好受。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師做事雷厲風行，我很羡慕老師的果斷，而且，結果告訴我，老師總是對的。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為他曾經也錯過太多。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾麗妮忽然有一種錯覺，自己面對的，不是一個嚴厲的聖徒，而是一個遲暮的老人。"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我和達里奧一起前往伊比利亞之眼，他恐怕不會犧牲。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#5$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......在黃金船上，那個怪物告訴我老師的死訊時，她說，老師的死毫無意義。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我對她說，審判庭不存在“無意義的犧牲”。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但在那之前，老師曾經教過我，死得其所是一種將死亡浪漫化的說法。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少對審判官來說，只有活下去，才能履行自己的信念。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以在說老師的死有意義之前，如果老師能夠活著，那就更好了，我是這麼想的。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "達里奧把你教得很好。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那場災難席捲整個伊比利亞之後，審判庭在我與其他聖徒的帶領下，逐漸形成了現在的規模。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們做成了許多事，那些事你大多能在經卷上讀到。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但其中總有一些事，讓我去思考剛才那樣的問題——如果我那樣做了，是否某個人，甚至某些人可以不用死。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#7$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但即便我能夠做到許多事，我也只是一個人，或許我做了另一個選擇，反而會導致另外的傷亡。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#7$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您在告誡我，個人的力量是有限的。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道你的辭職竟然是因為對審判官的道路感到失望？", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然不是......只是我沒想到這就被您看穿了。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果是那樣，從斯圖提斐拉號回來的時候，我就應當從你身上看到畏縮。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你沒有。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的堅定比之格蘭法洛初見時還要純粹。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我又怎麼會懷疑你在退縮？", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是......", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還記得，幾年前，達里奧告訴我，他的第一個學生，會是一個年幼的孩童。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了審判庭的延續，每一個大審判官都需要從審判官中挑選幾個學生，將自己的所學傳承下去。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，一個孩童，十分少見。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "經卷拯救了我的生命，但如果沒有老師發現我，我可能也會死在那座廢墟裡吧。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，我被送到了審判庭的孤兒院中，從那時起，老師偶爾會來看一看我。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......老師並不是立刻成為我的老師的。實際上，身為大審判官，按照規定他也不應該教當時身為孤兒的我。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但當他知道我立志要成為一名審判官，並且已經開始接受訓練之後，過了一段時間，他忽然告訴我，他會親自教授我一些東西。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#4$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我對這件事也一直有些疑問，所以後來我找了一個機會詢問他這件事，他當時說的話，我至今都記得很清楚。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g16_lighthouse_street", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#1", "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼決定讓你成為我的學生？", "name": "大審判官達里奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為你對於審判庭的熱忱，對於經文與律法的熱情，傳到了我的耳中。", "name": "大審判官達里奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的嗎？！", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#6$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#2"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而這是你最大的弱點。", "name": "大審判官達里奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#2"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#2"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的正義來源於那本拯救了你的經卷，來源於審判庭對你的養育，來源於你成為審判官道路上的學習。", "name": "大審判官達里奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#2"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卻不來源於你的雙眼見過的景色，你的雙耳聽過的話語，你的雙腳走過的土地。", "name": "大審判官達里奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#2"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在還太過脆弱，艾麗妮。", "name": "大審判官達里奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#2"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.5, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g26_dusk_wild", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這段話我當時沒有理解，老師也不願意多說，我就一直記著。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到現在，我才理解了老師這麼說的原因。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他害怕我因正義而盲目，因激進而受傷，並因真相而夭折。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為我曾是那麼地相信律法與經卷中的內容就是我的一切。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以......你開始懷疑審判庭的律法有其侷限性。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#2$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我依然認為律法行之有效。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想說審判庭的正邪之分過於粗暴。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#2$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我相信我們的準則經歷過考驗。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然如此，你又為什麼要離開審判庭？", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#10$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師曾經告訴我，在那一刻來臨時，我必須是伊比利亞最後的防線。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾經覺得，老師對我的要求太高，但現在我卻明白，這是他對我最不值一提的要求。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這並不是因為我天賦異稟，也不是因為我肩負著獨一無二的使命。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只因為他這麼想，並且在這麼做。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我身為他的學生，也應當這麼做，僅此而已。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在斯圖提斐拉號上懂得了，老師對我的一切教誨，到最後都是要我明白一點——", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "經文與律法將指導我的行動，但我的行動首先必須遵循我自身的想法。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#6$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我必須自己理解，自己相信，然後，經文與律法才會真正成為我的力量，提燈才能真正震懾那些海怪。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#6$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在審判庭底下的囚籠見過了真相，更在斯圖提斐拉號上認識了它們的思考與語言，甚至——進化。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#6$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我因此看清了我的敵人，也理解了我們所面臨的危機。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我與那些獵人同行，和她們共同作戰，瞭解了她們的傲慢，但也看到了她們的強大之處。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她們是未知的，卻不一定是可怕的。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，經歷了這一切，孩子，你得出的答案，究竟是什麼？", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#10$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在真正直面那些怪物的那一刻終於明白，我懷疑過的，也是老師懷疑過的。我擔心過的，也是老師擔心過的。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的正義曾經經不起考驗，老師的強硬卻是他深思熟慮的結果。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不再懷疑，不再猶豫，不再逃避，我要去做我能做，我應該做的事。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#6$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，對不起，卡門閣下，我好像說了許多不敬的話......", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，請您相信，我辭去審判官的職務，是為了更好地履行審判官的職責！", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "審判官的職務太過敏感，只有辭去審判官的職務，才能與其他組織，甚至國家開展交流。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子，你看到了合作的曙光。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離開審判庭後，你打算怎麼做？", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會先嘗試與那三個深海獵人共同行動一段時間。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#6$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她們似乎和那個叫羅德島的組織聯繫相當密切，我也在考慮要不要和那個組織進行合作。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#6$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果是這樣的話......", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#9$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你都聽到了，凱爾希。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1#4", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦？！", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1#4"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，但剛才的一段對話相當精彩，讓我忍不住駐足傾聽。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1#4"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔欸......", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1#4"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以及，羅德島自然不會拒絕與一名出色的前審判官合作。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1#4"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾麗妮，你可以辭去審判官的職務，但這並不意味著你需要離開審判庭。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？！", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你將成為審判庭的信使前往羅德島，代表審判庭與羅德島進行合作。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的嗎？", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記住，艾麗妮，你今天做出的決定，將會成為阿戈爾與伊比利亞合作的第二步。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是！", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#5$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去吧，做好出行的準備。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這趟新的旅途無人為你引航，但你心中的信念將會為你指引道路。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4009_irene_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是！", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#5$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 300.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看啊，凱爾希。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對我而言，阿戈爾與伊比利亞合作的契機在此刻出現，已經太晚太晚。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即便它確實帶來了些許轉機，歲月在我身上留下的痕跡，也讓我無法從中感到絲毫歡欣。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而對她來說，卻竟如黎明曙光。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果它們的進化是生命的本能，那眼下，這個女孩所做的選擇，無疑是文明的本能。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯？", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在看什麼？", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#10$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g26_dusk_wild", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "BackgroundTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "yFrom": 0.0, "xTo": 100.0, "yTo": 40.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.2, "yScaleTo": 1.2, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "順著凱爾希的目光看去，老人看到，擺放在達里奧墳前的提燈，忽然閃爍了幾下。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 23.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "像是在道別，又像是在送行。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 23.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "sto